Package allpeople

Class Person

java.lang.Object
allpeople.Person
Direct Known Subclasses:
Faculty, Student
public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
The Person class is a representation of a person. It contains all the basic information about a person. It includes their name, contact information, address, and a personal id
Since:
11/29/2020
